<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vale Hotels</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/img/images/logo.svg" alt="">
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Calendar</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Destinations</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="hero">
            <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 1.svg" alt="Hotel Background">
            <div class="booking-form">
                <div class="date-picker">
                    <label for="from-date">From</label>
                    <input type="date" id="from-date">
                </div>
                <div class="date-picker">
                    <label for="to-date">To</label>
                    <input type="date" id="to-date">
                </div>
                <button type="button">Schedule</button>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="features">
            <div class="image-collage">
                <img src="/img/landing/Pexels Photo by Chait Goli.svg" alt="Living Room">
                <img src="/img/landing/Pexels Photo by Dom J.svg" alt="Towels">
                <img src="/img/landing/Pexels Photo by Adrian Mohammad.svg" alt="Plant">
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="suite-container">
            <img src="/img/landing/Rectangle 47 (1).svg" alt="Suite de 2 Quartos e 1 Banheiro" class="suite-background">
            <div class="suite-text">
                <h1>2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom</h1>
                <p>Experience the perfect blend of comfort and style in our spacious two-bedroom suite, designed to
                    cater to
                    both relaxation and functionality. Ideal for families or groups, this suite features a modern
                    bathroom
                    equipped with luxurious amenities.</p>
                <p>Unwind in the cozy ambiance of our well-appointed bedrooms, each offering plush bedding and ample
                    storage
                    space. Make yourself at home and enjoy a memorable stay with us!</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="reviews">
            <h2>What they say about us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to our Reviews section! Here, you can read about the experiences of our guests who have stayed at
                our hotel. We value feedback from all our visitors as it helps us continuously improve our services and
                ensure a memorable stay for everyone.</p>
            <div class="review">
                <p>“We had an absolutely wonderful stay at the Vale Hotel! The staff was incredibly attentive, and the
                    rooms were spotless and comfortable.”</p>
                <strong>Jessica M. - Sete Barras, SP</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="review">
                <p>“Our room had a fantastic view of the ocean and was equipped with all the amenities we needed. The
                    rooftop pool was a highlight, offering a relaxing atmosphere and stunning views.”</p>
                <strong>Liam T. - Iguape, SP</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="review">
                <p>“Vale Hotel exceeded all our expectations! The decor is modern yet cozy, and the beds are super
                    comfortable.”</p>
                <strong>Sophia L. - Ilha Comprida, SP</strong>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="unique-experience">
            <h2>Unique experience</h2>
            <div class="experience-gallery">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 9.svg" alt="Experience Image 1">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 2.svg" alt="Experience Image 2">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 7.svg" alt="Experience Image 3">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 8.svg" alt="Experience Image 4">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 5.svg" alt="Experience Image 5">
                <img src="/img/landing/pexels-pixabay-258154 6.svg" alt="Experience Image 6">
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <section id="location">
        <h2>Find Us Here</h2>
        <img src="/img/landing/image 2.svg" alt="Map showing the location">
    </section>
    <section id="contact">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <div>
                <h3>Address</h3>
                <p>Av. Clara Gianotti de Souza, 612 – Centro, Registro – SP, 11900-000</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Contact</h3>
                <p>WhatsApp: (13) 99661-1415</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Follow Us</h3>
                <p>
                    <a href="#">Instagram</a> | 
                    <a href="#">Facebook</a> | 
                    <a href="#">WhatsApp</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>© 2024 Vale Hotels. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>